Class AnalyticsSessionEvent

java.lang.Object
  com.appglu.AnalyticsSessionEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class AnalyticsSessionEvent
extends Object
implements Serializable

Represents an event that happened during the usage of the app. An event could be, for example, the tap of a button or the appearance of a dialog, etc.
An event can contain parameters and is used to collect mobile app usage statistics.

1.0.0
